oundaries , but this contradicts the whole theory of evolution , because by definition things ca n't happen quickly . ^ i only make these  um points because they relate to the geological record , and the age of the earth ; there are many other personal problems i could raise with evolutionary theory , but that is for another day . ^  ame</text_normal></message_body></message>